title: Make Yourself at Home, 3x2, At Willina Ranch, You Won't Be Let Down!
posting_body: You will feel at home at
Are you searching for a great apartment or townhome in Bothell, Washington?
Look no further than Willina Ranch Apartments!
Our community's ideal location gives you instant access to Interstate 405, allowing for an easy commute to Bellevue, Redmond, and Woodinville.
Nearby is an abundance of shopping, restaurants, and entertainments venues, and Saint Edward State Park is only minutes away.
Experience a lifestyle of convenience and comfort.
At Willina Ranch Apartments, you have the option of one, two, and three bedroom apartments and townhomes for rent.
Each home features a gas fireplace, plenty of natural lighting, a microwave, walk-in closets, a dishwasher, and an in-home washer and dryer.
Select spaces have hardwood flooring, a deck, extra storage, and a garage.
As a pet-friendly community, we invite you to bring your pets along.
We can't wait to welcome them home!
As a resident, you will enjoy quality community amenities at your disposal.
Enjoy a relaxing day at the shimmering swimming pool, soothing spa, or clubhouse.
We offer package receiving, on-site maintenance, and state-of-the-art fitness center.
Schedule a tour at Willina Ranch Apartments in Bothell, WA, and discover the many reasons why you will want to call us home.
